title: Close-up of a Sea Snail
description: A close-up view of a sea snail resting on sandy ocean floor. The snail has a spiral shell with brown and cream stripes, and its head is partially visible with tentacles extending.

title: Sustainable Development Concept
description: The image depicts a hand holding a transparent globe with a green infinity symbol, symbolizing sustainability. Surrounding the globe are icons representing various aspects of sustainability, such as recycling, industry, shopping, and waste management, all set against a backdrop of green grass and natural light.
